✅ Exercise 2
🔹 Code
for p in model.parameters():
    p.requires_grad = False

for p in model.fc.parameters():
    p.requires_grad = True


🔹 Answer
Only final layer trains


✅ ✅ ✅ FINE‑TUNING
✅ Exercise 1
🔹 Question
Unfreeze layer4

🔹 Code
for p in model.parameters():
    p.requires_grad = False

for p in model.layer4.parameters():
    p.requires_grad = True

for name, p in model.named_parameters():
    if p.requires_grad:
        print(name)

🔹 Answer
Layer4 is trainable

🔹 Difference
Transfer → final layer only
Fine‑tuning → deeper layers also



✅ ✅ ✅ CONCEPTUAL (ONE LINE)

TF‑IDF → importance
Word2Vec → context vectors
GloVe → global embeddings
Embedding → numeric words
Cosine → similarity
Classification → labels
Self‑Attention → focus
Transformer → attention model
Transfer Learning → reuse model
Fine‑Tuning → retrain layers